@startuml
object Teacher
object AttendanceController
object UpsertAttendanceUseCase
object AttendanceWriter
object ClassroomWriter
object TransactionWriter
object Database <<database>>
Teacher --> AttendanceController : 1: attendance command
AttendanceController --> UpsertAttendanceUseCase : 2: execute
UpsertAttendanceUseCase --> AttendanceWriter : 3: load session/class/student
AttendanceWriter --> Database : 4: SELECT validation rows
UpsertAttendanceUseCase --> AttendanceWriter : 5: load enrollment at session time
UpsertAttendanceUseCase --> AttendanceWriter : 6: save manual attendance
AttendanceWriter --> Database : 7: INSERT/UPDATE attendance
UpsertAttendanceUseCase --> ClassroomWriter : 8: sync fee projection
ClassroomWriter --> TransactionWriter : 9: write fee record
TransactionWriter --> Database : 10: UPSERT/DELETE fee
UpsertAttendanceUseCase --> AttendanceController : 11: summary
@enduml
